snippet: Denver sack-leader Von Miller aims to land a one-two punch in the Super Bowl as the number two pick of the 2011 NFL Draft tries to disrupt Carolina quarterback Cam Newton, that draft's number one overall choice....
lead_paragraph: Denver sack-leader Von Miller aims to land a one-two punch in the Super Bowl as the number two pick of the 2011 NFL Draft tries to disrupt Carolina quarterback Cam Newton, that draft's number one overall choice.

headline.main: Pass Rushing Miller in Top-Of-Draft Duel With QB Newton
